# Vercel Web Analytics Installation Report

## Summary
Verified and confirmed that Vercel Web Analytics is **already properly installed and configured** in this Next.js project.

## Current Implementation Status

### ✅ Package Installation
- **Package**: `@vercel/analytics` (version 2.0.1)
- **Location**: Listed in `package.json` dependencies
- **Status**: Already installed

### ✅ Configuration
- **Framework**: Next.js 16.1.1 with App Router
- **Integration File**: `External/app/layout.tsx`
- **Implementation**: Following official Vercel documentation guidelines

### Code Implementation
The Analytics component is correctly implemented in the root layout:

```typescript
// External/app/layout.tsx
import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next";

export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
  return (
    <html lang="en">
      <body className={`${inter.variable} antialiased`}>
        {children}
        <Analytics />  // ✅ Properly placed at the end of body
      </body>
    </html>
  );
}
```

